name: Burnside
description: Getting to the top is hard. Staying at the top is even harder. Sometimes it means you gotta burn that midnight oil. So if you’re running low and you need to bring the heat then get your glow up with Burnside. All day, all night, 24/7/365.  It’s another collectable trading card in the Los Demonios Amigos series. New cards drop every Tuesday.  Collect ‘em, trade ’em, get ‘em all! Keep an eye on Twitter for rare 1 of 1 color variants and remixes dropping randomly! Check me on IG and @losdemoniosamigos and @marksarmel and twitter @marksarmel. Website at marksarmel.com
